      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i just really cant go right now. it's so much trouble with the traffic here in mumbai and i'll just end up waiting hours in a clinic. honestly it feels more like a heavy chest feeling rather than a true emergency. if i take some extra of my old medicine and maybe some of those herbal steam puffs my neighbor uses, can i just wait a few days to see if it settles down? it's probably just stress or something.",
